Nta ngurube zemewe

Mu myaka yashize, itsinda ryâ€™inyamaswa zifite amahembe ziyeyemeje gukora ibirori bikomeye hejuru yimisozi. 
Zatumiye  izindi nyamaswa zifite amahembe zonyine.

Ingurube imaze kumva ibyibyo birori, iriyumvira iti: "ko nta mahembe mfite. Nzakora iki?"

Bukeye, yagize igitekerezo. Yashyize amahembe ku mutwe n'ibishashara!

Ingurube yumvaga ifite ubwenge cyane igihe yemererwaga mu kirori. Ikibazo nuko ibirori byaberaga hafi yizuba.

Igihe ibirori byatangiraga gushyuha, ibishashara byatangiye gushonga amahembe aragwa.
Inyamaswa zifite amahitamo zaratangaye. Ziribaza ziti "Uyu ninde utagira amahembe? Kuki yaje hano?" .

Umwami w'inyamaswa ategeka ati: "Mufate iyo ngurube muyijugunye ku isi." Bafashe ingurube bayijugunya hasi.

Ingurube ikennye! yaraguye,igusha izuru ryayo hasi. Kandi izuru ryayo ryahise ririgita.

Ntuzatangazwe rero no kubona ingurube ryayo riringaniye, kuva kera.
